    </ol>
    <div class="carousel-inner">
        <div class="item active">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAIAAACQd1PeAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAARnQU1BAACxjwv8YQUAAAAJcEhZcwAAHYcAAB2HAY/l8WUAAAAMSURBVBhXY2DvOA8AAfgBX6YQ3XkAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="First slide">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Always connected, always on-line – never compromising</h1>
                    <p>
                        Thanks to its cost-effectiveness, Accelrys Notebook Cloud (previously Contur iLabber Cloud) is the perfect option for any organization looking for rapid deployment and adoption, with no investments needed and minimum operating costs.
                        <br />
                        <br />
                    </p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="#overview" role="button">View details</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAIAAACQd1PeAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAARnQU1BAACxjwv8YQUAAAAJcEhZcwAAHYcAAB2HAY/l8WUAAAAMSURBVBhXY2DvOA8AAfgBX6YQ3XkAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="First slide">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Take Accelrys Notebook Cloud for a Test Drive</h1>
                    <p>
                        Take a 2-week test drive with a free team evaluation of Accelrys Notebook Cloud. You'll be surprised how easy it is to use and how quickly your team will become productive.
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        <br />
                    </p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/Home/FreeTrial" role="button">Sign up today</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="item">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAIAAACQd1PeAAAAAXNSR0IArs4c6QAAAARnQU1BAACxjwv8YQUAAAAJcEhZcwAAHYcAAB2HAY/l8WUAAAAMSURBVBhXY2DvOA8AAfgBX6YQ3XkAAAAASUVORK5CYII=" alt="First slide">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="carousel-caption">
                    <h1>Serious about Security</h1>
                    <p>
                        Hosted in a state-of-the-art SAS 70, Type II compliant data center, using some of the most advanced Internet technology to keep your data safe and protected at all times.
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        <br />
                        <br />
                    </p>
                    <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="/Home/Security" role="button">Learn more</a></p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left"></span></a>
    <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right"></span></a>
</div><!-- /.carousel -->

<div class="container marketing">

    <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img src="/Content/Images/cloud.png" alt="Overview" style="height: 100px;">
            <h2>Overview</h2>
            <p>
                Set up your own cloud-based ELN system and be up and running within minutes, letting you focus on what is important - more innovation and less administration.
                <br />
                <br />
            </p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="#overview" role="button">View details &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img src="/Content/Images/team.png" alt="Free trial" style="height: 100px;">
            <h2>Free Trial</h2>
            <p>Take a test drive with a free team evaluation of Accelrys Notebook Cloud. You'll be surprised how easy it is to use and how quickly your team will become productive.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/Home/FreeTrial" role="button">Sign up today &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
        <div class="col-lg-4">
            <img src="/Content/Images/padlock.png" alt="Security" style="height: 100px;">
            <h2>Security</h2>
            <p>
                Hosted in a modern, state-of-the-art, data center. We use some of the most advanced Internet technologies to keep your data safe and protected at all times.
                <br />
                <br />
            </p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="/Home/Security" role="button">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
        </div><!-- /.col-lg-4 -->
    </div><!-- /.row -->
