            <p>
                <b>Make the Paperless Lab Transition</b>
                <br />An ELN that’s easy to USE and DEPLOY for any discipline, any organization
            </p>
            <p>
                <b>Focus on the Science</b>
                <br />Replace paper notebooks and eliminate time-consuming and error-prone manual searching and documentation
            </p>
            <p>
                <b>Low TCO, fast ROI</b>
                <br />Flexible, subscription-based license model with no hardware investments or IT resources needed
            </p>
            <p>
                <b>Flexible, Easy to Use and Deploy</b>
                <br />Deploy quickly and get teams up to speed and productive immediately due to an intuitive and user-friendly interface, whilst also gaining an electronic notebook that meets the demands of today’s global enterprise
            </p>
            <p>
                <b>Collaborate Instantly</b>
                <br />Easily store, search and share all notebook entries from any location
            </p>
            <p>
                <b>Protect Your IP</b>
                <br />Digital signatures, experiment templates and work-flow alerts ensures maximum IP protection and regulatory compliance
            </p>
            <br />
            <p>
                Interested in having it in-house? <a href="http://accelrys.com/products/eln/contur/accelrys-notebook.html
" target="new">Click Here</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img class="featurette-image img-responsive" src="/Content/Images/screenshot.png" alt="Screenshot">
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

    <div class="row featurette img-responsive">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <a href="https://www.sciencecloud.com/" target="_blank"><img class="featurette-image" src="/Content/Images/sciencecloud.png" alt="ScienceCloud"></a>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Transform Scientific Collaboration</h2>
            <p>Or use Accelrys Notebook Cloud as part of ScienceCloud, an ecosystem of collaborative, cloud-based tools to help transform the way you run your externalized R&D project: multiple collaborators, single platform, one conversation.</p>
            <a href="https://www.sciencecloud.com/" target="_blank">Learn more</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="featurette-divider">

