            <p>All plans include daily backups, unlimited storage, 24/7 Support, all software updates and online training</p>
            <p>Move easily between the different cloud plans by adding and renewing seats via your online admin</p>
            <p>Only pay for active seats, whilst still having access to all of your group’s past experiments</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-xs-3"></div>
                <div class="col-xs-3"></div>
                <div class="col-xs-3 popular pricingcell">&nbsp;</div>
                <div class="col-xs-3"></div>
                </div>
